caption.title: Phylogenetic tree.
caption.p: Maximum likelihood tree of 731 DENV-1 E gene sequences (1,485 bp) including 15 new sequences from this study (red bold), 33 sequences from previous study in Bhutan (blue), 3 vaccine strains sequences (black bold and italics), and 680 other sequences from GenBank (black). Bootstrap values are indicated at the major nodes.
